Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.62,0:00:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊 吊上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百年前沉入海底的宝箱终于让我们吊上来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.41,0:00:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 慢点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静 冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这所谓的宝箱 怎么又长又窄的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.02,0:00:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 吊得太高了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.28,0:00:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 放下来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.19,0:00:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快撬开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个箱子从里面上锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管毛啊 砸开就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 好像有什么字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-I-O 迪奥 是名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.27,0:01:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就天黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候就看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.01,0:01:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我去拿焊枪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.71,0:01:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要跟宝物见面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某天 一艘无人游艇被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.22,0:01:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船没有发生故障
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.78,0:01:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有打斗的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.66,0:01:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船上只有三杯剩下一半的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.96,0:01:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其余的 就只是一个被乙炔焊枪烧开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突兀地放置在甲板上的铁箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱内空空如也
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.74,0:01:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人惊异的是 箱子的双层构造如同防空洞一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们纷纷猜测是发现宝物了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数月后 也慢慢地遗忘了
Comment: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空条承太郎 17岁 身高195cm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.30,0:02:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲是日本人 爵士音乐家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在举行巡回演出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲是英裔美国人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 承太郎是我儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(530,650)}Kuujo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(750,650)}Jotaro
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校的朋友取空条的Jo和承太郎的Jo叫他JoJo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承太郎杀了几个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.06,0:02:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 我不要听我不要听
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 谁说过他杀人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.96,0:02:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是打架
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他打的几个混混都带着双节棍和小刀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.92,0:02:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那四人里面还有人打过拳击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那四个人加起来一共有15处骨折
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卵蛋也被抓爆…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都送医院了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:02:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太 你要叫他好好反省啊 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:02:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 问题是之后的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份拿去复印传阅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你儿子还真怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进 我领你去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 总之你带他回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？已经能出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不能一直让他呆在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 太太你的日本话很流利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本住了多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我们这里也忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拘留所都要排着队进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你儿子就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 承太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承太郎 把球扔给妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的运动会要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要庆祝呢 今天想吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.62,0:04:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈做的菜就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵不吵！
